page.title: 04Norton & Lenchwick People
page.content: On the 8.5.85 2 adults did these activities: C. Got up at 08.00 and had cereals, toast & fruit juice.For Lunch: Cauliflower Cheese,Toast,Fruit Salad, Ice Cream,Tea.For Dinner:Bread Rolls, Jam,Cheese,Strawberries,Yoghurt,coffee Listened to Radio 2 & Radio 4.Read Daily Telegragh.Went Strawberry picking.Played golf.Visited friends. Bought groceries,toiletries & fruit. D. Got up at 07.15 and had toast and coffee for breakfast.She cooked it. She had other meals at 13.00 and 17.30.At 13.00 she had sandwiches and at 17.30 she had sausage and potatoes. She did not watch any programmes on television that day.She listened to MIKE READS breakfast show on Radio 1. She did not read a newspaper or book.She went to work and College.She went to Norton club in the evening.
